        <h2>4. What the Service is — and what it isn't</h2>
        <p>PoopCheck is a <strong>wellness tracker</strong>. You can use the Service to capture images of your stool and record symptom and lifestyle context, receive AI-generated Wellness Feedback, track changes over time, and take part in optional features such as community participation, chat, or Premium content.</p>
